disusered:
iOS returns the token on success, but Android sends it in a push notification after the "OK". I addressed it by listening to the push notification event:

``` javascript
$rootScope.$on('pushNotificationReceived',
  function androidRegistration(event, data) {
    var token = data.regid || undefined;
    return token;
  }
);
```
